commands: NODE_ENV=test NODE_OPTIONS="--max-old-space-size=8192" nx database:reset > reset-logs.log && NODE_ENV=test NODE_OPTIONS="--max-old-space-size=8192" nx jest --config ./jest-integration.config.ts
nx run twenty-zapier:build && cp -r ../twenty-shared/ node_modules/twenty-shared && zapier push --skip-npm-install

npx concurrently --kill-others --success=first -n SB,TEST 'nx storybook:serve:static twenty-front --port={args.port}' 'npx wait-on tcp:{args.port} && nx storybook:test {projectName} --shard={args.shard} --checkCoverage={args.checkCoverage} --port={args.port} --configuration={args.scope}'

npx concurrently --kill-others --success=first -n SB,TEST 'nx storybook:serve:static twenty-ui --port={args.port}' 'npx wait-on tcp:{args.port} && nx storybook:test {projectName} --shard={args.shard} --checkCoverage={args.checkCoverage} --port={args.port} --configuration={args.scope}'
